author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall ceiling tips…just one way of doing it. I like Crack Tape because it’s strong when combined with setting type joint compound. Quick Set Lite 20 sets up fast and allows for multiple coats in one day. And I’m using Level 5 drywall tools because they don’t rust and have perfect flex for smooth work 🔥#drywall #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
